<li><cite id="CITEREFBhattacharya2000">Bhattacharya, T (2000), <a href="http://www.homepages.ucl.ac.uk/~uclyara/bong_us.pdf" class="external text" rel="nofollow">"Bangla (Bengali)"</a>, in Gary, J. and Rubino. C., <i>Encyclopedia of World's Languages: Past and Present (Facts About the World's Languages)</i>, WW Wilson, New York, <a href="/wiki/%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B7:BookSources/0824209702" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0824209702</a><span class="printonly">, &lt;<a href="http://www.homepages.ucl.ac.uk/~uclyara/bong_us.pdf" class="external free" rel="nofollow">http://www.homepages.ucl.ac.uk/~uclyara/bong_us.pdf</a>&gt;</span></cite>.</li>
<li><cite id="CITEREFBaxter1997">Baxter, C (1997), <i>Bangladesh, From a Nation to a State</i>, Westview Press, <a href="/wiki/%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B7:BookSources/0813336325" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0813336325</a></cite>.</li>
